{"tid":1847943,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"1。28林奠記者會重點","createTime":"2020-01-28T09:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T11:47:17.000Z","uid":258106,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea04f0423b369146483e697bccb2c76c06182be","tid":1847943,"uid":258106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:04:52.000Z","msg":"⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️⭕️<br />\n1） 減少口岸人流<br />\n支那聲稱會暫停發出自由行簽証<br />\n（之前批左果D唔影響）<br />\n商務旅行唔受影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）暫停高鐵、直通車、支那渡船<br />\n來往支那飛機、巴士班次減少<br />\n（唔係暫停）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3）暫時停止口岸服務<br />\n西九、紅磡、沙頭角、文錦渡（客運）<br />\n1月30日凌晨開始<br />\n（其他口岸繼續開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4）離境體溫驗測<br />\n<br />\n5）非本地居民收錢（唔講明醫武肺 收唔收...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6）叫海外香港人番黎香港 （做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n7）呼籲私人企業比員工在家工作 （呼籲炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8）乘搭公共交通工具<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">戴口罩</span></strong><br />\n禁蒙面法fail <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9)  接觸在港湖北人 （接觸炸，無野就繼續比佢地周街走<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10）隔離營放棄粉嶺暉明邨<br />\n「暫時」未有其他屋邨使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n11）防疫物資全球搜羅 （無details)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n❌❌❌❌❌❌❌❌❌❌❌❌❌❌❌<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n無封關<br />\n無停市<br />\n無叫人出街就戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nPS 林奠自己連口罩都唔識戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tV1P5Kb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtV1P5Kb.png&h=c56ebc1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0a3808780a46e293637bf70a5da44f525fb6612","tid":1847943,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T09:05:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">匿埋喺屋企出唔到街？<br />\n唔夠口罩唔敢出去？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Twitter 戰線永遠需要你！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">入去 <a href=\"http://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=65f2eb75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a> 撳 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">/task2</span></span> 拎任務</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\nTask 2 好缺人，大家快啲去幫手！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，撳幾個掣都做唔到？<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n1. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1221867978716844032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1221867978716844032&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtb0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=e4a76905\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioP